Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 一万圆也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱借给你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子和家具都被拿去抵挡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我一定会还你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 祐司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格直呼我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.40,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 之前你们花了我多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说你已经忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是穷光蛋 咱们没什么好谈的	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前因为你是有钱人家少爷才跟你混的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点都感觉不到 真白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧 稻垣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已予受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}扯开的线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.70,0:04:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死后灵魂将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了三天 觉得怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赌哪个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出这么点儿押他不会解开绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这可不是闹着玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不懂得幽默的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了啊 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 百忙之中打扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样 久违的老家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老样子气氛凝重令人不快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣总编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你也留下的话当个副编不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能当个副编啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,销量不错啊 最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}国际慈善家的真面目\N和平党片冈洋三的\N纸醉金迷的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖福 还凑合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.00,0:07:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型经济政治杂志什么时候堕落成丑闻杂志了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个口不饶人的家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际慈善家的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平党片冈洋三的纸醉金迷的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是揭发了事实真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说由于这篇报道片冈被逮捕了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得个警视总监赏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你能比这个写得更好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是为了这个事情叫你来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是想找些快乐的旧事聊聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作想交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我盯着国民党的河原崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和背景复杂的的女人在交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证给你不错的报酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来威胁的把柄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用词可要小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作为最后的王牌而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们得到了内部消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河原崎他很谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用堂堂正正的方法无法揭露他的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会帮这个忙的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想趟这混水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把现有的资料准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期限是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周以内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能搞到的证据不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就适当夸张一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编造吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是编造的也有不错的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算再窘迫也是个记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把人看扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要耍花招的话你自己想办法去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装酷了 我可把你全调查清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在干把偷拍的照片卖给本人这种事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的朋友在拜托你帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也想威胁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落了啊 稻垣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和以前一样没毅力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为贫穷的生活会让你成熟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙可出不了头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么样都无所谓啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.20,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目标更重要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种天真的披露报道没可能吸引读者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 一脸看上去就不像好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.80,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么天气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再闯进来就把你送到警察局去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见下稻垣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要见的话就事先预约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能预约我早预约了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 滚远点 人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.30,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找稲垣有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是在那工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟稻垣一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和我聊聊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣他人怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片冈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片冈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 难怪感觉在哪里见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是片冈洋三的儿子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为受贿而被捕的那个和平党的那个片冈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他被搞得身败名裂就是因为你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还吸过毒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是捏造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没吸过毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被陷害的 被稻垣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实在警察进行药物检查时是阴性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那篇报道中也说证据确凿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙 是稻垣他随便乱写出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然立刻登出了修正启事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时老爸的受贿事实已被公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成了相当大的舆论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为都被重大事件分散了注意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正启事我也完全没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣那家伙全都算计到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.60,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财产都被查封 家人也都变得四分五裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是那个家伙的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了加罪于爸爸 稻垣甚至连我们家人也利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能让这家伙逍遥地活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不能放过夺走我一切的这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做你也只会被当作是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以委托了别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇解决不了任何问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把那份能量用在自己身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.10,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化悲愤为力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再考虑下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在抛弃人生还太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.20,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他喝饮料反而还受他气 真不划算啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的他怎么可能有那种钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的真不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常了不起啊 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个都可以拿到我们店里去卖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是照着店长教的做而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸会高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才开始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子和梓我带走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 到你家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么妈妈 我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微振作点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很精神吗 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那家伙真的委托了别人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 在这种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 我又看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 在个热闹的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热闹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么标志性的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快餐 蓝宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.10,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是片冈洋三的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错 我家都变的不像样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢蛋 理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你老爸做了那么多坏事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪你爸去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了揭发我老爸 竟然利用我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是干什么的啊 那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找错对手了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣可是空手道入段的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你委托的是地狱少女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.10,0:16:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长先回店里去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 我去帮你拿杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我是半信半疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得不可能存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女是真的存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪遇见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你委托她杀了稻垣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在却是你自己行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.70,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇明明是委托地狱少女 怎么还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约的信物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要解开这根线 契约就成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.20,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 还来得及啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不要解开线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去让稻垣谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻垣死了也不能解决任何问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将他所作的事情都公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报道我来写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你千万不要解开线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是什么人为何要做这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我敢断言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了 一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 和一个十分妖艳的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去我们店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啊 那走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们当什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真是个偏僻的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪点不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦 请打开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身酒臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沦落的新闻界!\N真 实 的 内 幕!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让我从这出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你们让我出去啊 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己所犯的罪有些忏悔了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪 什么罪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把被隐藏的真相公诸于世而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称赞我还差不多 根本没有理由把我称为罪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那就是说为了真相不管做什么都无所谓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揭露的真相才是正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你所谓的新闻工作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.80,0:20:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 民众所追求的就是名为真相的轰动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在满足民众的那种欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.20,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说呢 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船开回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.90,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.20,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开线了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.90,0:22:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在把一切公诸于众又有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.20,0:22:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎的东西已经难以复原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有家人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.80,0:22:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该明白吧
